answer_B:
为了化简给定的分式 a \left( \frac{1}{a-1} - \frac{1}{a^2-1} \right) \div \frac{a^2-a}{a^2-1}
1. 化简括号内的表达式。
2. 化简除以分数的运算。
3. 合并并化简得到的表达式。
\frac{1}{a-1} - \frac{1}{a^2-1}
\frac{a+1}{(a-1)(a+1)} - \frac{1}{(a-1)(a+1)} = \frac{a+1-1}{(a-1)(a+1)} = \frac{a}{(a-1)(a+1)}
a \left( \frac{a}{(a-1)(a+1)} \right) \div \frac{a^2-a}{a^2-1}
a \left( \frac{a}{(a-1)(a+1)} \right) \times \frac{a^2-1}{a^2-a}
a \left( \frac{a}{(a-1)(a+1)} \right) \times \frac{(a-1)(a+1)}{a(a-1)}
a \left( \frac{a}{(a-1)(a+1)} \right) \times \frac{(a-1)(a+1)}{a(a-1)} = \frac{a \cdot a \cdot (a-1)(a+1)}{(a-1)(a+1) \cdot a \cdot (a-1)} = \frac{a}{a-1}

